social_posts.post_text:
And… just like that, my collegiate career has come to an end. My volleyball experience has been a rollercoaster from the start, but truly from the bottom of my heart. Penn State Volleyball has healed any wounds and covered up my scars. This team and I mean every single one of them, from staff to players - has made my last collegiate year one to remember for the rest of my life. I appreciate my team for going hard for me no matter what, the most genuine team I’ve ever had. I love you all to the moon and back. 

Thank you Penn State Volleyball for making my dreams come true. 

On to my next chapter… 🫶🏿 

With Love, 
Kashauna Williams
